name: C# Numbers Program
body:
### Welcome to the Official C# Numbers Program!
I have made some really cool mathematical programs including collatz conjecture, fibonacci, and more for c#. Go ahead and check it out. See if you can disprove the collatz conjecture,or figure out patterns in the sequences, and even take crazy factorials. It's all there! Please give me feedback on what you want to see or change!

### Authors and Contributors
Michael Bilenko (@mbilenko03)
Brandon Richards (@bren1337)
